---
title: Services
layout: default
---

<div class="pt-10 bg-gray-900 sm:pt-16 lg:pt-8 lg:pb-14 lg:overflow-hidden">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-md px-4 sm:max-w-2xl sm:px-6 sm:text-center lg:px-0 lg:text-left lg:flex lg:items-center">
        <div class="lg:py-16">
          <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-blue-500
            sm:mt-5 sm:text-6xl lg:mt-6 xl:text-5xl">
            <span class="block">Account for your present</span>
            <span class="pb-3 block text-yellow-500 sm:pb-5">Maximize your future</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg xl:text-xl">
            For nearly 100 years and four generations, <b>Buckley &amp; Sitzman,
            LLP</b> has guided clients like you through the dynamic accounting
            landscape, helping them to maintain financial viability while
            proactively planning for future goals.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10">
            <a href="/contact-us" class="inline-flex items-center uppercase py-6
                     px-8 rounded-md text-lg
                     hover:bg-yellow-600 bg-yellow-500 text-white font-medium
                     focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
                     focus:ring-yellow-400 focus:ring-offset-gray-900">
              Get in Touch
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 -mb-16 sm:-mb-48 lg:m-0 lg:relative">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-md px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-0">
          <img
            class="w-full max-w-md h-auto"
            src="/img/header-illustration.svg" alt=""
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-16 text-center">
  <h1 class="text-4xl tracking-tight leading-10 font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl sm:leading-none md:text-6xl">
    {{title}}
  </h1>
</div>

<div class="relative py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="prose prose-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-500 mx-auto">
    <p>
      At Buckley &amp; Sitzman, LLP, we guide our clients through a full range
      of tax planning and preparation decisions with strategies that minimize
      your tax liabilities, maximize your cash flow and keep you on track to
      your financial goals. Our expertise, experience, analysis and thorough
      research allow us to optimize financial opportunities to be found in
      existing as well as recently altered tax laws. We are knowledgeable and up
      to date on the tax laws and can make sense of your receipts, bills and
      notices.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mx-auto px-4">
  <ul role="list" class="space-y-12">

    {%- set services = collections.services | first -%}
    {%- for service in services.data.items -%}
      <li class="">
        <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
          <h2>
            {{service.title}}
          </h2>
          <div>
            {{service.body | markdown | safe}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="relative my-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="prose prose-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-500 mx-auto">
    <p>
      We work tirelessly to ensure the best outcomes for our clients. Ready to
      see what the accountants and staff at <b>Buckley &amp; Sitzman, LLP</b>
      can do for you and your business?
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-prose text-center mx-auto">
    <p class="mt-10">
      <a
        href="/contact-us"
        class="inline-flex text-white items-center uppercase py-3 px-4 rounded-md
               hover:bg-blue-600 bg-blue-500 font-medium
               focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
               focus:ring-blue-400 focus:ring-offset-gray-900"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
